## Part 2

### Topic

**Describe a time when you started using a new technological device (e.g. a new computer or phone).**
You should say:

* what device you started using
* why you started using this device
* how easy or difficult it was to use
* and explain how helpful this device was to you.

### Candidate

I’d like to talk about the time when I started using a new laptop a couple of years ago. Before that, I had been using an older computer for quite a long time, but it had become very slow and unreliable. It often froze when I opened several programs at the same time, which was really frustrating, especially when I needed it for studying.

So I decided to buy a new laptop mainly because I needed something faster and more efficient for my academic work. As a student, I often have to search for information, write assignments, attend online classes, and sometimes even do some basic programming, so having a good computer is extremely important for me.

At first, it was actually quite easy to use, because the general functions were similar to my old device. However, there were still a few things I had to get used to, such as the new operating system layout and some shortcut settings. It took me a few days to feel completely comfortable with it, but overall, the learning process was not difficult.

This laptop has been incredibly helpful to me. It has made my work much more efficient, saved me a lot of time, and reduced a great deal of stress. I can study more smoothly, store my files properly, and use multiple applications without worrying that the system will crash. So overall, starting to use this device made a big difference in my daily life.

### 翻译

我想讲的是几年前开始使用一台新笔记本电脑的经历。
在那之前，我已经用了很久一台旧电脑，但它变得非常慢，也不太稳定。
当我同时打开多个程序时，它经常会卡死，这让我非常沮丧，尤其是在我需要用它学习的时候。

所以我决定买一台新电脑，主要是因为我需要一台更快、更高效的设备来完成学业上的任务。
作为学生，我经常需要查资料、写作业、上网课，有时候甚至还要做一些基础编程，因此拥有一台好电脑对我来说非常重要。

刚开始的时候，其实并不难上手，因为大部分基础功能和旧设备是相似的。
不过，还是有一些地方需要适应，比如新的操作系统布局，还有一些快捷键设置。
我花了几天时间才完全习惯它，但总体来说，这个适应过程并不困难。

这台笔记本对我的帮助非常大。
它让我的学习效率高了很多，节省了不少时间，也减轻了很多压力。
我可以更顺畅地学习、更好地保存文件，还能同时运行多个应用程序，而不用担心系统崩溃。
所以总体来说，开始使用这台设备对我的日常生活产生了很大的积极影响。

